label: SENT
text:
It doesn't hurt me, it's just difficult in the
     sense that I have to put a lot of money and effort to be eligible to
     visit the place again, so I really have to consider whether or not it's
     beneficial for me instead of investing those 100,000 in that, and I
     could start a small business here and maybe just thrive here.
name: Cuauhtémoc
